import React from 'react'
import { Image, Divider, Dropdown, } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import iunnologo from './iunnologo.png'

export default class Header extends React.Component {

    render() {

        return (
            <>
                <center>
                    <Divider hidden/>
                    <Image src={iunnologo} />
                    <Dropdown
    icon='filter'
    floating
    labeled
    button className='icon'>
    <Dropdown.Menu>
      <Dropdown.Item text='Cancel Order' />
      <Dropdown.Item text='Edit Profile' />
      <Dropdown.Item text='Sign Out' />
      
    </Dropdown.Menu>
  </Dropdown>
                </center>
                

        </>

        )
    }

}
